00:14.708 --> 00:16.410
MAKE ROOM, EVERYONE.
THIS IS MONICA.

00:16.443 --> 00:19.279
ALL RIGHT, WHO'S NEXT?
I'M FROM THE FUTURE.

00:19.313 --> 00:21.949
