00:31.125 --> 00:34.695
[ Sighing ] MM. YAEL.

00:34.728 --> 00:36.930
YAEL, YAEL, YAEL.

00:36.964 --> 00:38.599
SHE WAS
A RABBINICAL TEACHER.

00:38.632 --> 00:40.868
THE FUTURE IS
NOT IN DISPENSARIES.

00:40.901 --> 00:42.970
I WANT TO OPEN
SOMETHING BRIGHT.

00:43.003 --> 00:47.441
WE OFFER ONE BRAND ‐‐
OUR BRAND ‐‐ LIKE MILF,

00:47.474 --> 00:48.742
THAT YOU GROW.

00:48.776 --> 00:50.744
CAN YOU STILL GET YOUR SEEDLINGS
FROM THE LAB?

00:50.778 --> 00:54.014
I WAS FIRED YESTERDAY.
MM. NOT IDEAL.

00:54.048 --> 00:55.616
WELL,
WE'LL GO ELSEWHERE.

00:55.649 --> 00:56.984
ELSEWHERE?

