02:49.885 --> 02:53.188
NO, IT'S BETTER SHE WENT ALONE,
CONSIDERING THEIR...HISTORY.

02:53.222 --> 02:54.723
IS THERE ANYONE
ON THIS PLANET

02:54.757 --> 02:56.125
