OTHER THINGS ‐‐ GREAT THINGS.

03:02.297 --> 03:04.233
JOANNA?

03:04.266 --> 03:05.567
JOANNA.

03:05.601 --> 03:06.835
YOUR WIFE.

03:06.869 --> 03:09.405
OH. HER? NO, NO.
I'M TALKING ABOUT YAEL.

03:09.438 --> 03:11.573
YAEL,
AT RABBINICAL SCHOOL.

03:11.607 --> 03:13.642
YAEL OF SHARP TONGUE
AND EYEBROWS

03:13.675 --> 03:16.178
LIKE THE THROWING BLADES
OF THE MOSSAD.

03:16.211 --> 03:17.346
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:17.379 --> 03:18.580
THAT'S WHY
YOU TAGGED ALONG ‐‐

03:18.614 --> 03:21.717
TO BONE
SOME EX‐GIRLFRIEND?

03:21.750 --> 03:24.953
NOT JUST "BONE."
I'M‐A GET HER.

03:24.987 --> 03:26.688
THERE'S A REASON
THAT YOU NEED MILF SEEDS

03:26.722 --> 03:27.956
AND CONRAD
MOVED TO AGRESTIC.

03:27.990 --> 03:29.525
IT'S ALL PART
OF A BIGGER PLAN.

03:29.558 --> 03:30.759
IT'S CALLED
REGRESTIC NOW.

03:30.793 --> 03:31.894
YES, IT'S A REPRESSIVE,
SOULLESS,

03:31.927 --> 03:33.695
BROWN RECLUSE‐INFESTED
HELLSCAPE,

03:33.729 --> 03:35.431
BUT I WAS
ON A TRAJECTORY HERE,

03:35.464 --> 03:36.799
AND I THINK
THERE'S A POSSIBILITY

03:36.832 --> 03:41.303
THAT JOURNEY WAS TAKING ME,
COWED AND LIMPING,

03:41.336 --> 03:44.039
BACK TO HER ‐‐
BACK TO YAEL.

03:44.073 --> 03:45.841
YOU'RE LOSING IT.

03:45.874 --> 03:47.576
OR MAYBE
I'M FINDING IT.

03:47.609 --> 03:49.545
DO YOU GUYS
HAVE A RESTROOM?

03:49.578 --> 03:50.879
AND I'M THINKING

03:50.913 --> 03:53.248
MAYBE YOUR JOURNEY HERE
WASN'T FINISHED, EITHER.

03:53.282 --> 03:54.783
PLEASE.

03:54.817 --> 03:56.051
ASIDE FROM MY POT STRAIN,

03:56.085 --> 03:57.619
THERE'S NOTHING
BACK HERE FOR ME.

03:57.653 --> 03:58.954
HELLO?
[ TAPS DESK ]

03:58.987 --> 04:01.190
EXCUSE ME.

04:02.958 --> 04:06.862
SEE? BIGGER PLAN.

04:08.597 --> 04:11.667
Nancy: HERE'S STEVIE.
HE'S AT SOCCER CAMP.

04:11.700 --> 04:13.936
WE THINK
HE MIGHT GO PRO NEXT YEAR.
HE'S CUTE.

04:13.969 --> 04:15.938
I DON'T HAVE ANY MILF, OKAY?
I DON'T HAVE ANY MILF SEEDS.

04:15.971 --> 04:19.041
