FOR YEARS.

04:20.542 --> 04:21.877
YOU COULD HAVE
SAVED YOURSELF A TRIP.

04:21.910 --> 04:23.445
I KNOW YOU WORKED FOR HEYLIA
UNTIL A YEAR AGO.

04:23.479 --> 04:25.314
And I know you.
NO, THING‐‐

04:25.347 --> 04:26.849
YES, NO.

04:26.882 --> 04:29.051
THINGS HAVE CHANGED.
I'M IN THE HEALTH GAME NOW.

04:29.084 --> 04:31.153
HEALTH GAME?
THAT'S RIGHT. JUICE CLEANSES.

04:31.186 --> 04:33.689
GOT A HOOK‐UP WITH AN ORGANIC
FRUIT FARM OUT IN TEMECULA.

04:33.722 --> 04:35.257
PROFIT MARGINS
ARE UNBELIEVABLE.

04:35.290 --> 04:36.525
I WANT YOU
TO GROW FOR ME.

04:36.558 --> 04:37.793
WE'VE GOT
THIS CLASSIC DETOX, RIGHT?

04:37.826 --> 04:39.828
IT'S BASICALLY
CAYENNE AND ALOE VERA.

04:39.862 --> 04:41.130
GROW FOR ME.

04:41.163 --> 04:43.165
OR THE ROOT PROGRAM.
NOW, THE ROOT PROGRAM'S EASY.

04:43.198 --> 04:45.501
ALL IT IS IS CARROTS, BEETS,
ADDED CHLOROPHYLL.

04:45.534 --> 04:47.035
WE WERE GOOD TOGETHER.

04:47.069 --> 04:50.205
YES, LISTEN.
HERE'S THE FUNNY THING, OKAY?

04:50.239 --> 04:51.807
THE LIVER DOES AN INCREDIBLE JOB
OF ELIMINATING TOXINS

04:51.840 --> 04:53.809
SO BASICALLY THESE WOMEN
ARE PAYING ME $300

04:53.842 --> 04:56.412
TO DELIVER WISHES
TO THEIR HOUSE EVERY MORNING.

04:56.445 --> 04:58.046
YOU HAVE SOME,
DON'T YOU?

04:58.080 --> 04:59.515
SEEDS.

04:59.548 --> 05:01.917
IT DIDN'T MATTER.
EVEN IF I DID, WHAT WOULD I ‐‐

05:01.950 --> 05:03.485
NO, NO, NO!
BECAUSE ‐‐ NO, LISTEN!

05:03.519 --> 05:04.953
I AM DONE
WITH GROW‐HOUSES.

05:04.987 --> 05:06.288
I'M NOT
MAKING THAT MISTAKE AGAIN!

05:06.321 --> 05:07.623
YOU LET ME
WORRY ABOUT WHERE.

05:07.656 --> 05:09.725
DON'T WORRY ABOUT SHIT!
I AM NOT ‐‐ NO!

05:09.758 --> 05:12.561
I'M NOT LISTENING TO YOU.
I'M NOT LISTENING TO YOU.
YES, YES, YES, YES, YES.

05:12.594 --> 05:15.264
AAH! NANCY!

05:15.297 --> 05:16.565
UH, HI, PAM.

05:16.598 --> 05:17.733
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?!

05:17.766 --> 05:20.002
I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
IN AT LEAST A YEAR.

05:20.035 --> 05:20.936
OH, UH...

05:20.969 --> 05:23.639
MAYBE A LITTLE LONGER
THAN THAT.

05:23.672 --> 05:26.909
OH, SORRY, MEMORY'S FUZZY
FROM THE SHOCK TREATMENTS.

05:26.942 --> 05:29.111
GOOD NEWS ‐‐
THE SEX ADDICTION IS GONE.

05:29.144 --> 05:32.314
YOU AND CELIA ARE SO CLIQUEY,
I NEVER SEE YOU ANYMORE.

05:32.347 --> 05:33.715
ARE YOU COMING
TO THE WEDDING?

05:33.749 --> 05:36.118
WHAT WEDDING?
Alison: THERE YOU ARE.

05:36.151 --> 05:38.554
YOU HAVE TO WRITE CHECKS
TO THE CATERER, THE CAKE LADY ‐‐

05:38.587 --> 05:41.690
HI.
ARE YOU THE HARPIST?

05:41.724 --> 05:44.693
EXCUSE ME, MR. CONRAD, THEY
NEED TO MEASURE YOUR INSEAM.

05:44.727 --> 05:47.362
NO PROBLEM, LUPITA.
I'LL BE ‐‐

05:47.396 --> 05:48.997
AAH! iLA BRUJA!

05:49.031 --> 05:50.532
MY WEDDING.

05:50.566 --> 05:51.734
Alison: OUR WEDDING.

05:52.968 --> 05:57.906
DRIVING A KNOWN DRUG VEHICLE
WITH A BUSTED WINDSHIELD?

05:57.940 --> 05:59.641
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO IMPRESS MY GIRLFRIEND.

05:59.675 --> 06:02.644
WE KNOW ABOUT THE SCAM
AT THE IMPOUND LOT!

06:02.678 --> 06:04.113
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT A SCAM.

06:04.146 --> 06:06.949
WE HAVE THE NAMES.
TESTIFY ‐‐ INCIDENT EXPUNGED.

06:06.982 --> 06:09.685
OR YOU TAKE THE AUTO‐THEFT
CHARGE AND YOU DO SOME TIME.

06:09.718 --> 06:11.253
I'VE SEEN YOUR FILE,
BOTWIN.

06:11.286 --> 06:13.122
YOU COULD BE
A STAR ON THE FORCE.

06:13.155 --> 06:15.023
JUST GONNA THROW IT AWAY?

06:15.057 --> 06:17.559
FOR WHAT? OUELLETTE?

06:17.593 --> 06:20.963
HE'S A CROOKED, ALCOHOLIC,
WALKING ARTERIAL BLOCKAGE

06:20.996 --> 06:24.400
WHO DOES NOT
GIVE A SHIT ABOUT <i>YOU.</i>

06:24.433 --> 06:26.935
YOU HAVE 48 HOURS.

06:32.007 --> 06:34.510
MM.

06:34.543 --> 06:36.912
I'M EXPERIENCING
THE MOST POWERFUL DéJà VU.

06:36.945 --> 06:39.181
IT'S LIKE
YOU AND I WERE FROZEN,

06:39.214 --> 06:40.682
LOADED ONTO A UFO,

06:40.716 --> 06:43.685
FLOWN
10‐TO‐THE‐POWER‐OF‐9 PARSECS

06:43.719 --> 06:47.289
TO THE EARTH'S
DISTANT TWIN PLANET,

06:47.322 --> 06:49.558
AND REANIMATED
FOR THIS MOMENT.

06:49.591 --> 06:51.093
AND NOTHING'S DIFFERENT

06:51.126 --> 06:54.063
EXCEPT THIS PLANET
ROTATES WEST TO EAST,

06:54.096 --> 06:58.267
THE ATMOSPHERE HAS A LITTLE
MORE ARGON THAN WE'RE USED TO,

06:58.300 --> 07:03.539
AND YOU...HAVE BANGS NOW.

07:03.572 --> 07:04.840
I'M SORRY.

07:04.873 --> 07:07.576
DO YOU HAVE A CHILD
IN HEBREW SCHOOL?

07:07.609 --> 07:10.579
[ Chuckling ] NO.
NO, I DON'T HAVE...

07:10.612 --> 07:11.847
I DON'T HAVE A CHILD.

07:11.880 --> 07:13.582
YAEL,
DON'T YOU REMEMBER ME?

07:13.615 --> 07:17.086
IT'S ME, ANDY BOTWIN.

07:17.119 --> 07:20.823
NO. I'M SORRY.

07:23.992 --> 07:30.299
HIS NAME IS
LARS GUIN‐‐ GUINARD.

07:30.332 --> 07:32.701
HE DRIVES HOT RODS,
PLAYS GUITAR.

07:32.735 --> 07:35.304
FUCKING DUMB
AS A BAG OF ROCKS.

07:35.337 --> 07:37.573
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:37.606 --> 07:40.042
YOUR MOM
SHOULD BE LOCKED UP.

07:40.075 --> 07:43.445
OH, SHE WAS.
[ CHUCKLES ]

07:43.479 --> 07:47.716
SO, HOW DID YOU
END UP BACK HERE?

07:47.750 --> 07:50.953
I WAS LIVING IN NEW YORK
AFTER SCHOOL.

07:50.986 --> 07:55.624
I HAD THE SMALLEST APARTMENT
AND BROKE, SMELLY BOYFRIEND,

07:55.657 --> 07:58.660
BUT I LOVED IT.

07:58.694 --> 08:00.562
THEN MY DAD GOT SICK.

08:00.596 --> 08:03.298
I'M SORRY.

08:03.332 --> 08:05.701
[ SIGHS ]

08:05.734 --> 08:09.872
YOU KNOW, WHEN ‐‐
WHEN YOU LEFT ‐‐

08:09.905 --> 08:11.240
VANISHED ‐‐

08:11.273 --> 08:16.278
I...I THINK
I REMEMBER THE SIGN.

08:16.311 --> 08:19.915
I WAS HEARTBROKEN.

08:19.948 --> 08:25.821
MY PARENTS
WANTED ME AWAY FROM YOU.

08:25.854 --> 08:28.624
I POKED HOLES
IN OUR CONDOMS.

08:28.657 --> 08:32.294
THAT'S WHY
YOU GOT PREGNANT.

08:32.327 --> 08:33.762
I‐I WAS DESPERATE.

08:33.796 --> 08:38.133
I DIDN'T WANT YOU TO GO
TO PRINCETON AND LEAVE ME HERE.

08:38.167 --> 08:42.204
MEGAN, I'M ‐‐
I'M SO SORRY.

08:48.210 --> 08:49.912
WHAT THE FUCK?!

08:49.945 --> 08:52.381
I KNOW. I KNOW.
BUT I LOVED YOU AND...

08:52.414 --> 08:53.649
AND I LOVED YOU.

08:53.682 --> 08:56.618
I JUST LOVED YOU.
I LOVED YOU.

08:56.652 --> 08:58.620
YOU ARE THE ONLY GIRL
I EVER LOVED.

08:58.654 --> 09:01.223
STILL, TO THIS DAY.

09:01.256 --> 09:04.026
HOLY SHIT.

09:04.059 --> 09:09.364
I'VE NEVER LOVED ANYONE ELSE,
NEVER EVEN CAME CLOSE.

09:09.398 --> 09:13.102
FUCK.

09:13.135 --> 09:15.671
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

09:20.209 --> 09:22.077
[ SIGHS ]

09:25.881 --> 09:32.154
DO YOU STILL ‐‐
STILL LOVE ME?

09:32.187 --> 09:34.123
C‐COULD YOU?

09:34.156 --> 09:36.992
IS THAT RIDICULOUS?

09:37.025 --> 09:39.895
NO.

09:41.196 --> 09:44.032
IT'S NOT RIDICULOUS.

09:44.066 --> 09:46.034
[ SIGHS ]

09:46.068 --> 09:50.672
FUCK. [ SIGHS ]

09:54.009 --> 09:57.913
WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

10:02.351 --> 10:03.819
♪♪ AHH, AHH ♪♪

10:03.852 --> 10:09.158
♪♪ AHH, AHH, AHH‐AHH‐AHH ♪♪

10:09.191 --> 10:10.259
♪♪ AHH, AHH, AHH ♪♪

10:13.179 --> 10:15.748
WOW! WHERE'D YOU LEARN
TO BREAK LIKE THAT?

10:15.782 --> 10:18.151
OUR ROBOT BUTLER
TAUGHT ME.

10:18.184 --> 10:20.319
OH, RIGHT, RIGHT.

10:20.353 --> 10:22.922
BECAUSE YOU'RE FROM THE FUTURE.
[ SCOFFS ]

10:22.955 --> 10:25.158
OW!
YOU OKAY, DOUG?

10:25.191 --> 10:27.560
I DON'T THINK
MY FAMILY LOVES ME.

10:27.593 --> 10:29.729
YOUR WIFE AND KIDS?
OF COURSE THEY LOVE YOU.

10:29.762 --> 10:31.230
NO, FUCK THOSE GUYS.
MY SON'S AN ASS BANDIT.

10:31.264 --> 10:32.465
MY WIFE MARRIED
THE GRANDPA FROM "COSBY."

10:32.498 --> 10:34.200
AND MY DAUGHTERS
THINK I'M DOG SHIT.

10:34.233 --> 10:36.803
I'M TALKING ABOUT MY REAL‐LIFE
FAMILY ‐‐ THE BOTWINS.

10:36.836 --> 10:39.172
[ GRUNTS ]
I BOUGHT THEM THIS HOUSE,
AND THEY ALWAYS EXCLUDE ME,

10:39.205 --> 10:40.840
MAKE ME BABYSIT.

10:40.873 --> 10:42.842
SPEAKING OF WHICH,
IF YOU SEE A LITTLE MEXICAN KID

10:42.875 --> 10:46.179
IN A SOCCER JERSEY RUNNING
AROUND, GIVE A SHOUT‐OUT.

10:47.647 --> 10:49.549
WHERE ARE THEY NOW?

10:49.582 --> 10:52.418
TOOK OFF ON A VACATION.
DIDN'T EVEN TELL ME.

10:52.452 --> 10:55.421
DON'T WORRY, DOUG.
EVERYTHING GETS BETTER FOR YOU.

10:55.455 --> 10:57.190
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

10:57.223 --> 11:00.059
SOON, YOU BECOME
A VERY GREAT MAN.

11:00.093 --> 11:03.463
Man: OW!

11:03.496 --> 11:06.499
WALTZ POSITIONS, EVERYBODY.

11:06.532 --> 11:08.034
1, 2, 3, 4.

11:08.067 --> 11:10.103
SO, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

11:10.136 --> 11:12.238
ALISON LIKES THE 'BURBS.

11:12.271 --> 11:13.773
PRICES WERE LOW
AFTER THE FIRE,

11:13.806 --> 11:17.243
AND, WELL, I HAD A FEW
FOND MEMORIES OF THE PLACE.

11:17.276 --> 11:18.511
I BOUGHT YOU SOMETHING.

11:19.879 --> 11:22.015
IT'S 5 ACRES.
GOOD SOIL.

11:22.048 --> 11:23.516
PLUS, I'VE ENROLLED YOU

11:23.549 --> 11:26.319
IN THE SOUTHWEST COMPASSIONATE
COLLECTIVE, SO YOU'RE LEGAL.

11:26.352 --> 11:28.554
YOU BOUGHT
A PIECE OF LAND?

11:28.588 --> 11:31.157
MILF IS GONNA GROW HERE,
CONRAD.

11:31.190 --> 11:33.159
You're gonna make it grow.
THAT'S LOVELY.

11:33.192 --> 11:35.061
WOW, YOU GOT IT
ALL FIGURED OUT.

11:35.094 --> 11:36.596
ONE SMALL DETAIL.

11:36.629 --> 11:40.600
YOU CAN'T GROW IN THESE VALLEYS.
IT'S ALL OWNED.

11:40.633 --> 11:42.135
I BOUGHT IT.

11:42.168 --> 11:44.437
OWNED,
AS IN TERRITORY.

11:44.470 --> 11:45.905
GANGS.

11:45.938 --> 11:47.907
YOU HAVE TO PAY THEM A TAX.
THAT'S IF THEY EVEN OKAY IT.

11:47.940 --> 11:50.109
SO I'LL GO
TALK TO THEM.

11:50.143 --> 11:53.479
NO, YOU WON'T. 'CAUSE GUESS
WHO'S BACK IN CHARGE.

11:54.347 --> 11:56.315
HE'S OUT?
YOU'RE SURE?

11:56.349 --> 11:59.318
OH, YEAH. IT'S 2006
ALL UP IN THIS BITCH.

11:59.352 --> 12:01.454
THEY'RE RUNNING WITH
THE SAME CREW, SO IF I WAS YOU,

12:01.487 --> 12:03.322
I'D WORK ON THAT
GETTING‐OUT‐OF‐TOWN‐NOW THING.

12:03.356 --> 12:05.925
I LOOK FORWARD
TO A PHOTO.

12:05.958 --> 12:07.326
BE SAFE.

12:07.360 --> 12:09.128
YOUR TUITION CHECK
BOUNCED.

12:09.162 --> 12:10.296
GOD DAMN IT!

12:10.329 --> 12:14.167
THIS FUCKING WEDDING
IS KILLING ME.

12:14.200 --> 12:17.570
DO NOT
GO TO GUILLERMO.

12:20.073 --> 12:22.041
[ TRAIN WHISTLE BLOWING ]

12:22.075 --> 12:23.776
CHOO‐CHOO!
CHOO‐CHOO!

12:23.810 --> 12:25.044
[ Laughing ]
YEAH!

12:25.078 --> 12:26.512
Nancy:
CHOO‐CHOO!

12:28.014 --> 12:29.982
HEY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:30.016 --> 12:32.185
WHOSE BIRTHDAY
ARE WE CELEBRATING?

12:32.218 --> 12:36.456
OR IS IT, UM...
A QUINCEAÑERA?

12:36.489 --> 12:39.359
YOU GOT TO ADMIT,
YOU GUYS REALLY LIKE PICNICS

12:39.392 --> 12:42.128
SO SOMETIMES IT'S KIND OF
HARD TO IDENTIFY

12:42.161 --> 12:43.463
THE SPECIFIC OCCASION.

12:43.496 --> 12:45.565
ACTUALLY, THIS ONE'S
GONNA BE A FUNERAL.

12:49.068 --> 12:52.772
BE NICE.
WE'RE IN PUBLIC.

12:52.805 --> 12:55.708
[ SPEAKING SPANISH ]

12:55.742 --> 12:59.379
LET'S GO. LET'S GO.

13:04.017 --> 13:05.218
YOU KNOW,
I DON'T GET IT.

13:05.251 --> 13:09.255
MURDER, KIDNAPPING...
HOW DID YOU GET OUT?

13:09.288 --> 13:11.924
I HIRED ME THE LAWYER THAT
GOT JERRY SEINFELD'S WIFE OFF

13:11.958 --> 13:14.327
